title: How to Paint: Ice Covered Bases
description:
In this Warhammer Painting video, we'll be looking at how to paint ice-themed bases and get them looking awesome and on the tabletop in no time at all!      
  
If you're new to painting - check out our Citadel Colour Painting Essentials videos to learn all about it.
